Class HandshakeInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.springframework.web.reactive.socket.HandshakeInfo

  • public class HandshakeInfo

    Simple container of information related to the handshake request that started the WebSocketSession session.

    5.0
    Author:
    Rossen Stoyanchev
